"title": "5566: suffering, encouragements in",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5566: suffering, encouragements in",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Believers are encouraged by the loving care and faithful promises of God and by the example, support and prayers of fellow believers. The prospect of heaven helps them to endure.</p>\n<h2>The encouragement of God's love</h2>\n<h3>The care of the Father</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:13\">PSA 103:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:17\">PSA 86:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:10\">ISA 50:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:8-Isa64:9\">ISA 64:8–64:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:6-Luke18:7\">LUK 18:6–18:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:27\">JHN 16:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:11\">JHN 17:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:15\">JHN 17:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:32\">ROM 8:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:3\">2CO 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>The sympathetic understanding of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:18\">HEB 2:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:11\">ISA 40:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:3\">ISA 42:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:5\">ISA 53:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:18\">LUK 4:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1\">ISA 61:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:27\">JHN 14:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:22\">JHN 16:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:35-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:35–8:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:15\">HEB 4:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:25\">HEB 7:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:3\">HEB 12:3</a></p>\n<h3>The comfort of the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:16-John14:17\">JHN 14:16–14:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:13\">LUK 11:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:5\">ROM 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:26\">ROM 8:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22-Gal5:23\">GAL 5:22–5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:16\">EPH 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:14\">1PE 4:14</a></p>\n<h3>The promises of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:50\">PSA 119:50</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:28\">ROM 8:28</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:9\">2CO 12:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:10\">ISA 41:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:2-Isa43:3\">ISA 43:2–43:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:31-Matt6:33\">MAT 6:31–6:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:4\">ROM 15:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:7\">PHP 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:10\">1PE 5:10</a></p>\n<h2>The encouragement of the fellowship of believers</h2>\n<h3>Examples from the past</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:1\">HEB 12:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:17-Ps102:18\">PSA 102:17–102:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:11\">JER 20:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:11\">PHP 4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:25-Heb11:26\">HEB 11:25–11:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:10-Jas5:11\">JAS 5:10–5:11</a></p>\n<h3>Support from other believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:11\">1TH 5:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:13\">RUT 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:11\">JOB 42:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:15\">ACT 28:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:4\">ROM 16:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:6-2Cor7:7\">2CO 7:6–7:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:14\">PHP 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:11\">COL 4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:11-1Thess2:12\">1TH 2:11–2:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:18\">1TH 4:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:9\">2TI 4:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:11\">2TI 4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:13\">PHM 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:25\">HEB 10:25</a></p>\n<h2>The encouragement of looking ahead</h2>\n<h3>The assurance of victory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:37\">ROM 8:37</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:20\">ROM 16:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:20\">1CO 15:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:25\">1CO 15:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:55-1Cor15:57\">1CO 15:55–15:57</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:16-1Thess4:17\">1TH 4:16–4:17</a></p>\n<h3>The prospect of glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:18\">ROM 8:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:25-Job19:26\">JOB 19:25–19:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:17\">ISA 65:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:17-2Cor5:1\">2CO 4:17–5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:6-2Thess1:7\">2TH 1:6–1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:13\">2PE 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:24-Jude1:25\">JUD 1:24–1:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:16-Rev7:17\">REV 7:16–7:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:1-Rev21:4\">REV 21:1–21:4</a></p>",
